    <div class="trust-doc-section">
      <div class="trust-doc-section-title">2. Definitions</div>
      <ul class="trust-doc-list">
        <li><strong>“Account”</strong> means an individual user account used to access the Service.</li>
        <li><strong>“Workspace”</strong> means a tenant or organization space within the Service, typically representing a team or company.</li>
        <li><strong>“Workspace Owner”</strong> and <strong>“Admin”</strong> mean users with elevated permissions to manage settings, integrations, roles, and billing (as applicable).</li>
        <li><strong>“Viewer”</strong> means a user with read-only access to dashboards and content (as configured by the Workspace).</li>
        <li><strong>“Customer Data”</strong> means data submitted to or processed by the Service on behalf of a Workspace, including data from connected integrations.</li>
        <li><strong>“Content”</strong> means text, data, or other information processed through the Service.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="trust-doc-section">
      <div class="trust-doc-section-title">3. Eligibility and authority</div>
