        <li><strong>Account security:</strong> you agree to promptly notify us if you suspect unauthorized access to your Account.</li>
        <li><strong>One account per person:</strong> you will not share accounts or credentials with others.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="trust-doc-section">
      <div class="trust-doc-section-title">5. Workspace roles and administrator authority</div>
