        <li><strong>Responsibility:</strong> Workspace Owners/Admins are responsible for configuring integrations, access, and governance consistent with law and internal policy.</li>
        <li><strong>Viewer/member access:</strong> if you are a Viewer or standard user, your access may be limited by the Workspace’s configuration and your assigned role.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="trust-doc-section">
