      <ul class="trust-doc-list">
        <li><strong>Third-party terms:</strong> your use of third-party platforms is governed by the third party’s terms and policies.</li>
        <li><strong>Availability:</strong> third-party outages or API limitations may affect Service functionality.</li>
        <li><strong>Disconnect:</strong> Workspace admins may disconnect integrations to stop future ingestion.</li>
      </ul>

      <div class="trust-doc-links">
