        <li><strong>No interference:</strong> do not disrupt the Service, attempt denial-of-service activity, or abuse API/integration workflows.</li>
        <li><strong>No misuse for surveillance:</strong> do not use the Service for unlawful individual monitoring or targeting that violates policy or law.</li>
        <li><strong>No reverse engineering:</strong> do not reverse engineer the Service, including attempts to extract proprietary analytics methods or internal mappings.</li>
